{"tid":1169481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"EU駐港代表召見林鄭月娥 對逃犯條例提出外交照會 政府暫未有回應事件","createTime":"2019-05-24T12:11:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T12:56:14.000Z","uid":133680,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a195768b5294f3f8ba38eea01c49bf4ffa3bd8a6","tid":1169481,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:11:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190524/s00001/1558696748173/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%ad%90%e7%9b%9f%e4%bb%a3%e8%a1%a8%e6%99%a4%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad-%e7%99%bc%e5%a4%96%e4%ba%a4%e7%85%a7%e6%9c%83%e6%8a%97%e8%ad%b0%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190524%2Fs00001%2F1558696748173%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25ad%2590%25e7%259b%259f%25e4%25bb%25a3%25e8%25a1%25a8%25e6%2599%25a4%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad-%25e7%2599%25bc%25e5%25a4%2596%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e7%2585%25a7%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%258a%2597%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e4%25be%258b&d=vKriUNUS%2F8bMVR7j%2Bz3ffv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=4c0a5d73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190524%2Fs00001%2F1558696748173%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25ad%2590%25e7%259b%259f%25e4%25bb%25a3%25e8%25a1%25a8%25e6%2599%25a4%25e6%259e%2597%25e9%2584%25ad-%25e7%2599%25bc%25e5%25a4%2596%25e4%25ba%25a4%25e7%2585%25a7%25e6%259c%2583%25e6%258a%2597%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e4%25be%258b&h=ed9cc4fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190524/s00001/1558696748173/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e6%ad%90%e7%9b%9f%e4%bb%a3%e8%a1%a8%e6%99%a4%e6%9e%97%e9%84%ad-%e7%99%bc%e5%a4%96%e4%ba%a4%e7%85%a7%e6%9c%83%e6%8a%97%e8%ad%b0%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b</a><br />\n歐盟駐港澳辦事處及歐盟成員國的外交代表今日（24日）與林鄭月娥會面，表達對港府修訂《逃犯條例》的關注及擔憂，並正式發出表達抗議的外交照會，態度升級。<br />\n<br />\n辦事處主任卡諾（Carmen Cano）未有就會面作進一步評論，特首辦亦未回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，外交照會（Demarche）原義為「察照知會」，是外交上的正式文件，通常是兩個邦交國在交涉中，一國就某一事件的意見、態度或需要通知的事項，正式知會另一國的對等機構。通常只有在重大的事件中、或者是有重要意義的表態時，才會發出外交照會，多數是書面形式。<br />\n<br />\n收發照會者可以是機構名義，如外交部、大使館，或是具有外交性質的機構，如聯合國派遣機構；亦可以是個人名義，多數是外長、駐外使節。少數情况下，國家元首亦可發出外交照會。<br />\n<br />\n（路透社）"},{"pid":"42a2079a753a0f2a7a177dfba114ad43922e6e70","tid":1169481,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7adabbd2a1660b4fe0355eded97d16be9697e7f0","tid":1169481,"uid":5627,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦五毛狗"},{"pid":"fb3e4418cb587fcbda3f7f6094d186b16559eef6","tid":1169481,"uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7adabbd2a1660b4fe0355eded97d16be9697e7f0","tid":1169481,"uid":5627,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦五毛狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:14:23.000Z","msg":"三毛狗咁激動做咩，你撐支那港共扮香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d8a9b80891b29cc11e3f694fcae2bf870ef41e","tid":1169481,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb49a205dca3687c9ea1005e10fdb713ffd16c40","tid":1169481,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb3e4418cb587fcbda3f7f6094d186b16559eef6","tid":1169481,"uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7adabbd2a1660b4fe0355eded97d16be9697e7f0","tid":1169481,"uid":5627,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦五毛狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T12:14:23.0